. <a href=\"../../../Svalue/Make/index.html\" title=\"Soteria.Bv_values.Svalue.Make\"><code>Make</code></a> hash-conses the result. Called when an svalue carrying an extension is rebuilt (e.g. after its children are evaluated).</p></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-eval\"><a href=\"#val-eval\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> eval : <span><span>(<span><span><span class=\"type-var\">'g</span> <a href=\"#type-super_t\">super_t</a></span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><span class=\"type-var\">'g</span> <a href=\"#type-super_t\">super_t</a></span>)</span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><span><span class=\"type-var\">'g</span> <a href=\"#type-t\">t</a></span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><span class=\"type-var\">'g</span> <a href=\"#type-t\">t</a></span></span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p><code>eval eval_super x</code> returns <code>x</code> with every enclosing svalue nested in it replaced by <code>eval_super</code> applied to it — the extension's contribution to the <a href=\"../../../Eval/index.html\" title=\"Soteria.Bv_values.Eval\"><code>Eval</code></a> pass.</p></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-apply_subst\"><a href=\"#val-apply_subst\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> apply_subst : \u000A  <span><span>(<span><span class=\"label\">missing_var</span>:<span>(<span><a href=\"../../../../Symex/Var/index.html#type-t\">Soteria.Symex.Var.t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><span><span class=\"type-var\">'g</span> <a href=\"#type-super_ty\">super_ty</a></span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><span class=\"type-var\">'g</span> <a href=\"#type-super_t\">super_t</a></span>)</span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span>\u000A    <span><span class=\"type-var\">'subst</span> <span class=\"arrow\